{"tid":1556403,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有學校今日拖手出曬事","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T17:19:35.000Z","uid":271973,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79384a534ee7db4883194b015ea4ea96b5082e7b","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"新聞報左啦<br />\n但最出事係大家只係識拖學生妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔識投票選校董啊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家其實一定要做校友會成員<br />\n（唔係叫你上莊，做member ）<br />\n因為你會有票投校友校董<br />\n<br />\n而校董係唔洗搞活動<br />\n（校友會先係活動）<br />\n校董一年通常<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">開三、四次會</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而成為法團校董會既成員後<br />\n某程度大粒過校長<br />\n因為所有校長驚只有三樣野<br />\n一家長 ， 二教育局，三校董會<br />\n因為<br />\n校友校董係有能力投票同監察學校運作<br />\n<br />\n你估下咁多藍底學校驚唔驚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次多你一票多好多<br />\n<br />\n中學生師弟妹做左咁多<br />\n你班課又唔罷既大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工又唔罷既大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係咁都唔做掛<br />\n<br />\nP牌，求人幫推"},{"pid":"e2055cd79b065e0688453183618eb297ae643656","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6bd13de13a9cda6081930028bfd5f54aead4c480","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:00:47.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3bca899bf3b23ad817ecce22db1349442d452ba1","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"661318bdbf0be059817080d3d3093327391ef925","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:01:10.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"3f47abe2bb47be9856b13c8fb39cd68ba541b202","tid":1556403,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[全民和你唱]</span></span> 全世界全天候街邊唱香港國歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e81951b08020532261f2d0ebdded84c8fa879843","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"07f142b47abeba02c4fb294d6edd73c218de2a07","tid":1556403,"uid":6275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:01:52.000Z","msg":"邊間學校又唔開名"},{"pid":"6e655c21502ab3c7e17476d6c4c60613733640c0","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"68236ff8e0c7ed732c8deab3e9c50f98e8d37a46","tid":1556403,"uid":309888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18aae68ce0f3f714efe5d4bad52510b7f4afef9b","tid":1556403,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f142b47abeba02c4fb294d6edd73c218de2a07","tid":1556403,"uid":6275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:01:52.000Z","msg":"邊間學校又唔開名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2